deal.highlightsHtml: The entire family can enjoy an exciting day out interacting with animals, spectating shows, and experiencing thrilling coasters and rides!
deal.pitchHtml:
Highlights

  • ✓SeaWorld Admission Tickets, Dining Options or Fun Pass for Multiple Parks!
  • ✓Marine wildlife encounters with dolphins, sea lions and more!
  • ✓Family friendly fun with free admission for children two and under!
  • ✓All new summer celebration with dazzling drone shows and fireworks!
  • ✓Live entertainment, parades and immersive flying theatre experience!
  • ✓Hydrosurge cirque spectacular with dynamic dancers and acrobatics!
  • ✓Perfect for Gifting! Treat a loved one to an unforgettable experience!

Important Information — Groupon prices are inclusive of any applicable sales tax and there are no fees at checkout. The price you see is the price you pay!

What To Expect

Connect with amazing marine life up close and personal. Discover the wonders of the ocean through unforgettable animal encounters with dolphins, orcas, sharks, and more. From record-breaking roller coasters as Orlando's Coaster Capital to the kid-friendly rides of Sesame Street Land™, guests of all ages can enjoy attractions for every thrill level. The park's newest attraction, Expedition Odyssey – the most immersive multi-sensory Arctic flying theater experience ever created – is now officially open to all guests. Experience all-new animal presentations and shows at SeaWorld Orlando. Dive into the world of dolphins, orcas, and other marine animals like never before.

Seven Seas Food Festival

SeaWorld Orlando is turning up the volume in 2026 with its Seven Seas Food Festival concert series, featuring the strongest lineup of live music in the park’s history. Running select dates January 31 – May 17; the series features more than 30 full-length live concerts included with park admission, delivering a powerful mix of fan-favorite performers across multiple genres and generations.
The 2026 concert series kicks off in a big way with Flo Rida on January 31 and continues throughout the season with headlining performances from Boyz II Men, The Beach Boys, Trace Adkins, The Fray, Omar Courtz, Gene Simmons, Fitz and the Tantrums, Smash Mouth, Ying Yang Twins, Soulja Boy, and the Pop 2000 Tour hosted by Chris Kirkpatrick of *NSYNC, and many more.
Spanning six decades of music, featuring performers from the 1960s through today, the Seven Seas Food Festival concert series represents a wide range of genres including pop, hip-hop, rap, country, classic rock, alternative, hard rock, punk, Christian, and Latin.
The Seven Seas Food Festival is SeaWorld Orlando’s signature seasonal culinary celebration, featuring a NEW rotating lineup of global flavors, specialty beverages, and live entertainment throughout the park. Click here to view the full concert lineup and schedule.

Plan Your Visit

  • 
    Operating Hours Please check SeaWorld Orlando hours before your visit.
  • ♿
    Accessibility SeaWorld Orlando is a Certified Autism Center™, wheelchair accessible and welcomes service animals.

Ticket Options

Single Park Ticket + FREE $10 In-Park Spend

Valid for SeaWorld Orlando for one person. Valid on food, merchandise, animal tours, or toward any other purchase in park. Only one may be redeemed per transaction and must be surrendered at time of purchase. No change or credit given. Not redeemable for cash. No cash value. Non-refundable and non-transferable. If lost, damaged, or stolen these will not be replaced. Not valid with any additional discounts. Restrictions apply. Valid for date purchased only.

Single Park Ticket with All-Day Dining

Valid for SeaWorld Orlando for one person. All-Day Dining is valid only at SeaWorld Orlando participating restaurants and must be used by the same person.

SeaWorld Orlando Fun Card

Unlimited SeaWorld visits until 2026!

SeaWorld and Aquatica Fun Card

Unlimited visits to both SeaWorld and Aquatica Orlando until 2026!

2 or 3 Day Park Ticket

Valid for one person to any combination of SeaWorld Orlando, Aquatica Orlando, Busch Gardens Tampa Bay, or Adventure Island.

SeaWorld Orlando Silver Season Pass

Unlimited visits, free parking and no blockout dates! Plus discount on merchandise, one free photo digital download, and feeding encounters.

How It Works

1. Grab the Deal

Buy your Groupon first!

2. Redeem your Mobile Ticket

Scan your Groupon upon arrival.

3. Enjoy the Experience!

FAQs

When does SeaWorld Orlando open, and what are park hours?

SeaWorld Orlando typically opens between 9 am and 10 am, with closing hours varying seasonally. For precise park hours, check the official website before you go—especially on event days!

What should I pack for SeaWorld Orlando—any restrictions?

Pack essentials: sun protection, quick‑dry clothes (especially for Infinity Falls), water bottle, and waterproof footwear. Larger bags must be stored in lockers (available near major rides), while essentials can go in a small fanny pack.

Are there any SeaWorld Orlando tips for avoiding crowds?

Yes! Arrive early (30 mins before opening), visit on weekdays in off‑peak months like September or early November, and plan rides during animal shows to minimize lines. Consider Quick Queue to skip busy ride queues.

What are the top rides at SeaWorld Orlando in 2025?

Thrill‑seekers love coaster experiences like Mako, Kraken, Infinity Falls, and Ice Breaker. Families adore attractions like Journey to Atlantis and the newly popular Baby Shark live show, combining fun with marine education.

Where can I eat inside SeaWorld Orlando, and is dining covered?

SeaWorld Orlando offers various eateries in The Waterfront, expedition zones, and near major rides. You can buy an All‑Day Dining Deal for unlimited meals during your visit—ideal for families looking to dine without hassle.

For other SeaWorld park discounts see the below:

  • Busch Gardens Tampa
  • Aquatica Orlando
  • Adventure Island
